data.description: All Brick 3 bedroom 2 full bath Ranch in the coveted Boston Commons Subdivision at Fort Harrison.  Two car garage with side entry door.  Step into the massive open concept Great Room with 9 feet ceilings, Gas Fireplace, and built in surround sound speakers ready for your entertainment enjoyment.  Huge eat in Kitchen, timeless ceramic tile flooring, solid wood cabinetry with plenty of room for storage, including pantry and custom built in desk area.  Owners ensuite has large shower, linen closet and his and her walk in closets, one is off bathroom and the other is sliding mirror door inside the bedroom.  Large laundry room.  Huge sunroom with floor to ceiling windows, with attached composite decking,  with remote controlled retractable awning that gives you the option to block out the sun, surrounded by trees for your privacy and enjoyment. Newly painted Great Room and all 3 bedrooms.  Custom faux wood  blinds and six panel solid hardwoods doors thru out.  Washer, Dryer and Refrigerator are NOT included.  All other appliances will stay.  A Home to make your Own, at this price in the community, this home will not last long.
